{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, faculty were concerned about the potential for enforced use of AI detection tools.",
    "\"Turnitin will introduce its #AI detection tool…The speedy launch and lack of an opt-out have academics worried.\"",
    "Moreover, faculty were uneasy about the disinformation that may occur with the use of ChatGPT, a threat identified in the extant literature (Mhlanga, 2023).",
    "These concerns seem to mirror barriers Rogers (2003) found in technology adoption.",
    "For example, adoption barriers for ChatGPT could include perceptions that ChatGPT is not better than what supersedes it."
  ]
}